column7: THERE ARE SOME NOTES DOWN BELOW

I am going to model all the transfers as decision points. I will mark them these transfer points as *. The reason is that we want to capture the option of transferring without adding a node because those edges are required to travel.
column8: We are going to ignore the in station transfer points because we can't add them as edges since they aren't required to be travelled and we can't merge them into a single node because if we pass over that node once then we aren't stopping at all the stations.
